Key Dates for SR2012
====================

Tech Days
---------

[Tech Days](/schools/tech_days) take place throughout the year to help you along with the design and development of your robot.
The following dates are for the Southampton Tech Days. More Tech Days may be arranged in other locations at a later date.

 - [3rd December](/events/sr2012/tech_day_03_12)
 - 4th February
 - 17th March

Competition
-----------
[The Competition](/schools/competition) takes place at the University of Southampton over a period of two days.
This year the competition will be held on the 14th and 15th April.
